 it does compile and i used the svSetscope() mentioned in the DPI document
after calling it , it still gets a scope error:

Testbench C called 'initmem' but scope wasn't set, perhaps due to dpi import call without 'context', or missing svSetScope. See IEEE 1800-2017 35.5.3.

here is the task:

    export "DPI-C" task initmem;
    
    task initmem(input string file);
        /* verilator lint_off WIDTH */
        if (file != "") begin
            /* verilator lint_off WIDTH */
            $readmemh(file, cells);
            end else begin
            $display("file not exist");
        end
    endtask

